VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT SharedPreferences\.get.*\(".*"
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:(execute|query|rawQuery|execSQL|Runtime|ProcessBuilder|File\s*\(|URL\s*\() && MISSING:(validate|sanitize|escape|encode)
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Identifies the usage of Shared Preferences, which may contain untrusted inputs.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Untrusted Inputs: Shared Preferences.
